All right.

39:13.585 --> 39:15.654
Step into my office.

39:15.687 --> 39:16.121
(door creaks)

39:16.154 --> 39:18.390
The trailer.

39:19.758 --> 39:22.861
Would have expected more
from a Harvard man.

39:24.696 --> 39:27.132
You sit down and get relaxed,

39:27.165 --> 39:30.135
and we'll talk.

39:30.168 --> 39:32.838
Here comes the New Age
mumbo jumbo.

39:32.871 --> 39:34.406
I got no
mumbo jumbo.

39:34.440 --> 39:35.907
I'm just
gonna listen.

39:35.941 --> 39:37.543
About you

39:37.576 --> 39:39.110
and your mindset
with the upcoming trial.

39:39.144 --> 39:40.812
How you feel.

